<p><a name="Formulations_of_the_precautionary_principle" id="Formulations_of_the_precautionary_principle"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Precautionary_principle&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: Formulations of the precautionary principle">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Formulations of the precautionary principle</span></h2>
<table class="infobox nowraplinks" style="margin:0 0 1.0em 1.0em; border-spacing:0.4em 0; text-align:center; line-height:1.4em; font-size:88%;" cellspacing="" cellpadding="">
